\title{port: Certify Whether a Rounded Correlation Matrix Can Be PSD}
\description{
Given a reported correlation matrix whose off-diagonal entries are rounded
to a fixed number of decimals, \code{\link[=check_corr_psd]{check_corr_psd()}} decides whether \emph{any}
